dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Vilas County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This data group represent hydrography for Vilas County, Wisconsin in 2018, and includes the layers 'VILAS_HYDRO_2018_LINE', and ''VILAS_HYDRO_2018_POLY'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For complete metadata documentation, please visit https://maps.vilascountywi.gov/data.htmlThis data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2019. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2018. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2019.
